I'm still not really sure Queen Lagert
made the right decision there.

rows.label: tlk43310141_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I reckon it was Iira who attacked us
with that Judician Divine Beast weapon.

rows.label: tlk43310141_04_msg0003
rows.name:
It was the Superbians who brought it
back to life though, huh?

rows.label: tlk43310141_04_msg0004
rows.name:
If they'd have left it in the ground,
then Iira'd never have gotten their
hands on it.

rows.label: tlk43310141_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Those Superbian scum are just trying
to shift the blame over to Iira. We
shouldn't stand for it!
